          "meta": Map {},
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p>From the billions of photos uploaded to Flickr in 2018, we chose the <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157704759025571/\\">Top 25 Flickr Photos of 2018</a>. Of all the incredible moments captured, we’ve curated a list of the most inspiring photos, which represent a global community of unique perspectives.</p>
<p>To determine top photos, Flickr staff created an algorithm that took into account a number of social and engagement metrics, like how many times the photo was viewed or faved. We made sure to curate the raw data to avoid the results being a popularity contest; we removed spammers and photos that don’t qualify as high-quality. We also tried to ensure diversity of genre. For photographers whose photos placed in the top list multiple times, we selected their top-scoring photo.</p>
<p>We’re proud to present the Top 25 photos of 2018, whose diverse and talented photographers represent 12 different countries around the world.<br />
<br /></br></p>
<h2>Top 25 Photos of 2018</h2>
<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/marikoen/32647649804/\\" title=\\"Magic by marikoen, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2867/32647649804_0ed6882d46_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"683\\" alt=\\"Magic\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
<p><em>Magic</em> by <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/marikoen/\\">Koen Jacobs</a> (Belgium) with a Canon EOS 5D Mark III</p>
<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/dmtoh/38740240425/\\" title=\\"Blue and Gold by Dylan Toh, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4602/38740240425_96a243f1fd_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"512\\" alt=\\"Blue and Gold\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
