          },
          "meta": Map {},
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "We’re still accepting submissions for a few more days, so send us your celebratory photos (as long they were taken before January 1, 2019).",
        },
        "content" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "html",
            "xml:base" => "https://blog.flickr.net/en/2019/01/03/theres-still-time-your-best-shot-2018-ends-jan-7/",
          },
          "meta": Map {},
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/46588217211/\\" title=\\"There’s still time! Your Best Shot 2018 ends Jan. 7 by Flickr, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7869/46588217211_ab331bef6d_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"539\\" alt=\\"There’s still time! Your Best Shot 2018 ends Jan. 7\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
<p>You’ve set resolutions and said goodbye to a whirlwind year—but don’t close the door on 2018 yet! Take time to reflect, and submit your single best photo to the <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/groups/yourbestshot2018/\\">Your Best Shot 2018 Group</a> for a chance to win some sweet <a href=\\"http://blog.flickr.net/en/2018/11/28/your-best-shot-is-back-and-this-time-weve-got-prizes/\\">prizes</a>. We’re still accepting submissions for a few more days, so send us your celebratory photos (as long they were taken before January 1, 2019).</p>
<p>Visit our <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/groups/yourbestshot2018/discuss/72157704050751624/\\">FAQs</a> page for more contest info and be sure to <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/groups/yourbestshot2018/discuss/72157676152098098/\\">read the contest rules</a> before submitting.</p>
<p>Five (5) winners will be selected based on originality, creativity, and skill by SmugMug Inc. appointed photography professionals of the Flickr community. The winners will be notified by SmugMug Inc. on or about January 22, 2019.</p>
<p>Here is a selection of our favorite <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157704515204635/\\">wildlife</a>, <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157703406532791/\\">black and white</a>, and <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157699121913970/\\">architectural</a> shots from the group pool. Be sure to check out the entire galleries <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/\\">on Flickr</a>.</p>
<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157704515204635/\\" title=\\"Your Best Shot 2018: Wildlife, a gallery by Flickr, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4651/39581787014_5392a8dc37_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"625\\" alt=\\"Only You and Me Kid\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157703406532791/\\" title=\\"Your Best Shot 2018: Black and White, a gallery by Flickr, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1843/42503776120_d250faf72e_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"683\\" alt=\\"Unexpected rainfall\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157699121913970/\\" title=\\"Your Best Shot 2018: Architecture, a gallery by Flickr, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1960/44307527144_f08b005634_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"680\\" alt=\\"20180917-DSC06911\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
<p>Cheers to 2018,<br />
The Flickr Team</p>",
