        "summary" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "html",
          },
          "meta": Map {},
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Your Best Shot 2018 is in full swing: we’ve already received thousands of stunning submissions—photos that made you smile, cry, and grow. Check them out [&#8230;]",
        },
        "content" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "html",
            "xml:base" => "https://blog.flickr.net/en/2018/12/18/were-ready-for-more-submit-to-your-best-shot-2018-now/",
          },
          "meta": Map {},
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/45633937134/\\" title=\\"Haven’t submitted yet? by Flickr, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4887/45633937134_fcc379c093_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"539\\" alt=\\"Haven’t submitted yet?\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
<p><a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/groups/yourbestshot2018/\\">Your Best Shot 2018</a> is in full swing: we’ve already received thousands of stunning submissions—photos that made you smile, cry, and grow. Check them out <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/groups/yourbestshot2018/\\">here</a>. Haven’t submitted yet? You still have plenty of time to join in on the celebration: submit your single best shot of 2018 by January 7, 2019. Five winners will each receive a <a href=\\"https://www.peakdesign.com/collections/everyday-bags/products/everyday-backpack?utm_source=Flickr&amp;utm_medium=PartnerPromotion&amp;utm_campaign=FlickrPro\\">Peak Design Everyday Backpack</a>, a <a href=\\"https://www.smugmug.com/pro\\">SmugMug Pro subscription</a>, and lots of exposure on Flickr social media channels. Keep in mind, the sooner you submit to the Group, the more exposure your photos will get. </p>
<div class=\\"flickr-embed\\">
<div class=\\"flickr-image\\"><a data-flickr-embed=\\"true\\" href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickrdesign/45398294854/\\" title=\\"Your Best Shot 2018 - Prizes by Flickr Design Team, on Flickr\\"><img src=\\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4841/45398294854_0b4da2fe11_b.jpg\\" width=\\"1024\\" height=\\"539\\" alt=\\"Your Best Shot 2018 - Prizes\\"></a><a href=\\"\\"></a></div>
</div>
<p>Have questions about how we’re celebrating with your photos? Visit our <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/groups/yourbestshot2018/discuss/72157704050751624/\\">FAQs</a> page in the Your Best Shot 2018 Group and <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/groups/yourbestshot2018/discuss/72157676152098098/\\">read the contest rules</a> before submitting.</p>
<p>We are highlighting some of our favorite shots from the group across various themes, and these are some of the best <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/flickr/galleries/72157704515204635/\\">Wildlife</a> and <a href=\\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/soymae/galleries/72157704705469614/\\">Portrait</a> photos posted so far. </p>
<p>Cheers!<br />
The Flickr Team</p>",
        },
