          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>8:50pm PST</small> - Technical Summary:On February 21 between 7:00am PT to 9:20am PT, some users experienced connectivity issues with Slack.The connectivity issue arose from a misconfiguration that was discovered by our engineers. At 8:45am PT a change in the configuration led to users being able to successfully connect to Slack again.We’re hard at work on scoping preventative measures to ensure this doesn’t happen again in the future.</p><p><small>9:20am PST</small> - The issue some folks were running into with Slack failing to load has now been resolved. Thank you for your patience while we sorted that out.</p><p><small>5:52am PST</small> - Slack is not loading for a small number of people. We're sorry for the trouble - our team is working to find the cause and fix the issue.</p><p><small>4:50am PST</small> - We're currently looking into the reports of Slack not loading correctly for some people. Apologies for the disruption.</p>",
        },
