          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On February 21st at 4:22PM PST, we deployed a database change, which caused unexpected delays for processes such as notifications and link/image previews in Slack. The problem was identified and corrected, however a backlog of notifications and previews had formed in the meantime. We continued to monitor this backlog after the fix was implemented, and by 5:20PM PST, all functionality returned to normal.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "html",
          },
          "meta": Map {
            "br" => Array [
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
                "meta": Map {},
                "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
              },
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
                "meta": Map {},
                "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
              },
            ],
          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>6:52pm PST</small> - Technical Summary:On February 21st at 4:22PM PST, we deployed a database change, which caused unexpected delays for processes such as notifications and link/image previews in Slack. The problem was identified and corrected, however a backlog of notifications and previews had formed in the meantime. We continued to monitor this backlog after the fix was implemented, and by 5:20PM PST, all functionality returned to normal.</p><p><small>5:26pm PST</small> - We're seeing that push notifications are arriving on time once again. However, if you're still experiencing troubles, please let us know at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>5:15pm PST</small> - Push notifications may be running slower than expected. We’re investigating and will have an update shortly.</p>",
        },
      },
