          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On February 20th from 2:34PM PST, we began receiving reports from customers who were seeing a “For some reason, Slack couldn’t load” error when attempting to access Slack. By 7:34PM PST, we determined that everything was working as expected and all affected customers have been followed up directly for further investigation.",
