          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On February 13th at 5:02pm PST, we received reports that emails were failing to deliver to Slack forwarding addresses. We identified that this was the result of an expired certificate used to verify requests sent from our email provider. At 7:20pm PST, we deployed an update to address this. We identified that emails sent as early as 12:07pm PST may have been affected by this issue. Unfortunately, any emails sent via the integration during this time would not have been successful. However, they can now be manually re-sent.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "html",
          },
          "meta": Map {
            "br" => Array [
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
