          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>6:02pm PST</small> - We're aware of some issues with file uploads. For further troubleshooting, please reach out to feedback@slack.com, as we're happy to lend a hand.</p><p><small>12:34pm PST</small> - We have no new information to share just yet, but we'll provide more information as soon as it becomes available. We truly appreciate your patience.</p><p><small>12:03pm PST</small> - We’re still working on the file uploads issues at the moment, and we’re sorry for the interruption to your day.</p><p><small>11:33am PST</small> - Our team is continuing the investigation into this file upload problem. We hope to have a solution in place as soon as we can.</p><p><small>11:03am PST</small> - We're sorry to report that some folks may be having trouble uploading files at this time. Our team is working to resolve this as quickly as possible.</p>",
