              },
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
                "meta": Map {},
                "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
              },
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
                "meta": Map {},
                "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
              },
            ],
          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>6:03pm PST</small> - On January 30 at 8:40 PM PST, we internally detected an issue where customers were unable to sign into the Android app through Single Sign-On. Upon investigation, we determined that the issue was related to a recent browser release. On February 1 at 3:29 PM PST, we implemented a fix, so all customers should now be able to sign into Slack on their Android devices. If you are still having trouble, please let us know at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>4:05pm PST</small> - Thanks so much for your patience while our team addressed these issues with sign in on Android users. Everything should be working as it should once again, but if you run into trouble, please let us know at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>12:06am PST</small> - We believe to have narrowed the issue down to users on Chrome version 72. We do however have a workaround for the meantime. If you’re facing this problem, please try the following steps:1. Open a mobile web browser and navigate to your workspace URL2. Tap 'Sign in with [your identity provider]'3. Enter your username and password, then sign in4. Once signed in, tap 'Open Slack' under 'Have the app already?' to launch your workspace</p><p><small>10:25pm PST</small> - We've identified that this affects some Android app users signing in with their identity providers on Grid. We're continuing to investigate the issue.</p><p><small>9:22pm PST</small> - Some customers may have trouble signing in to the Android app through their identity provider. We're very sorry for the disruption — we're on the case.</p>",
        },
      },
      "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
