          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On January 7th, 2019 PT the execution of a weekly cleanup job errantly caused some Android users to be unable to receive notifications to their mobile devices.We manually reverted the errant changes made by the cleanup job, and by January 15th at 3:32pm Pacific Time all notification functionality was restored.",
