              },
            ],
          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On January 15th at 12:00pm PT, a code change to improve error messages in Slack caused some users to experience difficulties editing and uploading custom emoji. At 6:00pm PT we identified the affected deploy, conducted an investigation and reverted the deploy, resulting in all users being able to successfully edit or upload custom emoji by 8:00pm PT.We have implemented preventive measures to ensure this doesn’t happen in the future. If you are still having issues, please reach out to us at feedback@slack.com.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "html",
          },
          "meta": Map {
            "br" => Array [
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
                "meta": Map {},
                "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
              },
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
