          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On December 26th at 2:32 PM PST, we discovered that a small percentage of emails forwarded into some workspaces using our Email Ingestion feature were appearing blank. After investigating the issue, it was determined that the process responsible for handling these emails was occasionally failing and returning an empty file. A change was made to detect and retry the processing of any emails received in this state, and the Email Ingestion feature returned to full operation on December 28th at 1:43 PM PST.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
