            ],
          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>9:58pm PST</small> - Technical Summary:On January 3rd between 6:37pm and 8:01pm Pacific Time, we experienced an issue with our Google Calendar integration. This prevented new integrations from being configured and may have affected general Calendar functionality as well.After contacting Google we were able to deploy a fix and all normal functionality has been restored. If you are experiencing any continued issues, please reach out via feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>8:29pm PST</small> - All good! The Google Calendar integration is up and running again. Thanks for sticking with us!</p><p><small>7:22pm PST</small> - We're experiencing issues with the Google Calendar integration. We're currently investigating, and hope to have an update soon. Thanks for your patience.</p>",
