          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "We identified an issue with the file search function where files older than 2 weeks were not searchable in the index. We deployed a fix that restored the functionality. Please refresh Slack with Cmd/Ctrl + R to fetch the update. If you have any further hassles, please let us know at feedback@slack.com. Apologies for the disruption.",
