          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical summaryOn December 18 at 8:55am PT we experienced an event that resulted in one of our databases being overloaded. This led to longer than usual response times for various actions in Slack, for a small subset of workspaces.Our engineering team worked on implementing a fix, and functionality was restored to all workspaces by 10:05am PT.We’re currently investigating preventive measures to ensure that this doesn’t happen again. If you’re still running into any issues, please reach out to us at feedback@slack.com.",
