          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>2:04pm PST</small> - Technical Summary:On December 13th from 2:56pm PT until 4:57pm PT, we experienced an event that caused a significant increase in load on some of our databases. During this time, customers experienced slower-than-normal response times when searching members from their Admin pages.To resolve the issue, we implemented a short-term fix to reduce the load on the impacted databases. Full functionality was restored by 4:57pm PT. We are currently scoping preventive measures to ensure this doesn’t happen in the future. If you continue to have issues, please reach out to us at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>5:03pm PST</small> - We've resolved the problems with search and the workspace management services. Sorry for the disruption, and thanks for your patience with us. If you see any other problems, please reach out at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>4:45pm PST</small> - We're making changes to mitigate the impact of these issues and working towards a resolution. Thanks for sticking with us.</p><p><small>4:14pm PST</small> - We're continuing to look into the issues with search and the workspace management pages. Please bear with us.</p><p><small>3:43pm PST</small> - We're looking into an issue with search and workspace management services for some customers. We're terribly sorry for the disruption.</p>",
        },
      },
