          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On December 10th, 2018 at 5:31pm PT, a workspace deletion caused a spike in our job queue as the backlog of data was cleaned up.During this period, some users may have seen delayed link unfurls. We deployed a fix at 7:41pm PT and unfurls should be working as expected going forward.We also implemented a change to job queuing to prevent this from happening again. If you experience any issues, please let us know at feedback@slack.com.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "html",
          },
          "meta": Map {
            "br" => Array [
              Object {
                "attrs": Map {},
