          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:At 1:05 pm PT, we made a webapp deploy that contained a change in the Platform API for \`channels.join\`.Our Platform engineers noticed errors increasing for that particular endpoint and almost immediately, the culprit was identified.  At 2.54pm PT a forward fix was deployed.The fix was immediate and the all clear was called at 3.10pm PT.",
