          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "On November 20th at 2:35pm PT, we released a deploy which introduced an error in our code, which resulted in search failing for all users.At 3:37pm PT, we identified the affected deploy and reverted it. This cleared up the search errors, and all users were able to use search successfully again at 4:39pm PT.We’re very sorry to those affected for the disruption to your day. We’re investigating the root cause and making plans to ensure this doesn’t happen in the future.",
