          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On November 6th 2018 at 10:38 am PT, we began to receive reports that file uploads were failing in Slack for all customers.A recent change in our code had an adverse affect on file uploads, causing uploads to fail for 2 hours and 14 minutes. Once our engineering team discovered the issue, they reverted the code, and full functionality was restored for all customers by 12:55 pm PT. We called an All Clear at 1:21 pm PT.If you are still experiencing trouble please reach out to us at feedback@slack.com.",
