          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>9:23am PDT</small> - Technical Summary:On October 25th at 07:46 AM PT, we became aware of search issues in Giphy, which were affecting the Giphy integration in Slack. We reported the issue to Giphy, and they were able to resolve the problem. We called an all-clear at 08:30 AM PT. Slack customers should be able to use Giphy again, however if you’re still having trouble please reach out to us at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>8:31am PDT</small> - The issue with the Giphy integration appears to have been resolved. Thank you for your patience.</p><p><small>8:16am PDT</small> - We have received reports that some users are having trouble with the Giphy integration. This is something that we are monitoring, and we apologise for the inconvenience.</p>",
