          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On October 23 at 1:57 PM PT, we received reports that the Giphy integration wasn’t returning results as expected in Slack. We reported the problem to the Giphy engineering team and they were able to fix the issue. Giphy was back up and running by 2:53 PM PT.",
