          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On October 16th, 2018 between 11:55 AM and 12:50 PM PDT we experienced an internet connectivity issue with an external provider. This caused some customers to be unable to connect to Slack. The issue has been resolved and connectivity has been restored.",
