          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>10:31am PDT</small> - Technical Summary:On October 16th, 2018 between 11:55 AM and 12:50 PM PDT we experienced an internet connectivity issue with an external provider. This caused some customers to be unable to connect to Slack. The issue has been resolved and connectivity has been restored.</p><p><small>12:41pm PDT</small> - Thanks for your patience! We're happy to share that the connectivity issues impacting customers in Argentina should now be resolved. If you run into any trouble, please let us know at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>11:55am PDT</small> - Some folks in Argentina may be having trouble connecting to their workspaces at this time. Our team is investigating this now, and we'll share updates as soon as we can. Thanks for bearing with us.</p>",
