          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>12:54pm PDT</small> - Technical Summary:On October 16, 2018, at 8:06AM PT, we internally detected a problem with Duo Two Factor Authentication that may have prevented customers from authenticating into Slack. At 8:21AM PT, Duo posted a notice that they were investigating this issue. At 8:43AM PT, Duo resolved the issue and we called an all clear. If you have any trouble signing in to Slack, please get in touch at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>8:45am PDT</small> - The issues with Duo that may have been preventing some folks from authenticating into Slack have now been resolved. Thanks for sticking with us.</p><p><small>8:06am PDT</small> - Duo is currently experiencing issues which could prevent users from authenticating into Slack. We're sorry about any inconvenience this causes, and we'll provide updates as soon as we have them.</p>",
        },
