          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On October 8 from 1:36pm to 1:52pm PT, we detected some people were unable to send or retrieve messages in Slack. This was the result of a disruption to internet traffic external to Slack. The interrupted connections were automatically re-routed, and the ability to send and receive messages was restored by 1:52pm.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
