            },
          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>5:45am PDT</small> - Technical Summary:On October 7th at 3:43pm PT we detected a server had become unresponsive, resulting in a small number of workspaces being unable to create new Posts. The issue was resolved at 6:22pm PT when the server was restarted. We’re investigating the root cause, as well as making plans to ensure this doesn’t happen in the future.</p><p><small>6:37pm PDT</small> - Everyone should be able to create Posts as normal now. Thank you for holding tight. If you notice any further issues, please get in touch at feedback@slack.com.</p><p><small>3:43pm PDT</small> - We are aware of and investigating an issue with creating Posts. We're terribly sorry for the disruption to your workflow.</p>",
        },
      },
