          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<p><small>5:28pm PDT</small> - Technical Summary:On September 30th at 5:28pm PDT, we experienced a partial delay to some background Slack tasks, such as notifications and link unfurls.At 5:33pm PDT our engineers identified the issue and replaced the faulty server, resuming processing of the background tasks. By 5:50pm PDT, all new notifications were being delivered, and the all clear was called at 5:54pm PDT, August 10th.If you notice any further issues with background tasks such as notifications, link unfurls or reminders, please reach out to us at feedback@slack.com.</p>",
