          },
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On September 14th between 9:42am to 10:19am Pacific Time, we became aware of search issues in Giphy, which were affecting the Giphy slash command. We reported the issue to Giphy, and they were able to resolve the problem. We called an all-clear at 10:19am Pacific Time. Slack users should be able to use Giphy again, however if you're still having trouble please reach out to us at feedback@slack.com.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
