          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:On September 7th between 7:43am PT and 8:05am PT, Slack could not connect to our servers in the Sao Paulo region due to network issues. As a result, some people could not access their workspaces.At 8:05am PT we deployed a fix that would route users out of the troubled region and to a healthier server, which allowed people to successfully connect to Slack again.We are currently hard at work on scoping preventive measures to ensure this doesn’t happen in the future.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
