          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "Technical Summary:From 11:15am to 11:28am PT, 100% of customers were not able to use Slack.A deploy to our webapp to enable a feature for how we handle incoming connection requests referenced a function which wasn’t present in a specific file. This missing function caused all incoming requests to fail, returning connection errors to our users.We rolled back that change for all users at 11:26am. Users were able to receive responses from our app again by 11:28am.",
        },
        "content" => Object {
