          "value": "Technical Summary:At 12:21pm Pacific Time, we received notice from a third-party vendor that they were observing some issues with SMS services for some customers in Indonesia. This had the potential to affect Two-Factor Authentication messages for users trying to log in to Slack from this region.As we understand it, this third-party is working as fast as possible to restore all services in Indonesia. At this stage there are no indications that this has directly affected any Slack users, but if you are experiencing any issues please do reach out at feedback@slack.com.",
