          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<div xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\">End of April, beginning of May, it’s pretty well peak time for flowers.  Back in the last millennium, I used to run lots of flower pictures here, but they started blurring together in my mind in a way that made me not want to. But sometimes when the sun’s in just the right place, the flowers insist</div>",
        },
        "content" => Object {
          "attrs": Map {
            "type" => "xhtml",
