          },
          "meta": Map {},
          "ns": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<div xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\">I took my 12-year-old and 19-year-old to see<a href=\\"http://www.thesaucerfulofsecrets.com/\\">Nick Mason’s Saucerful of Secrets</a>tour (Lauren had choir practice). The band was grizzled, grey, and genial; when Nick closed by saying “We hope you had as much fun as we did” we felt he meant it.  Their stage banter  was that of well-bred Englishmen, dry and mild</div>",
        },
        "content" => Object {
